{"tid":1605300,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(重POST多圖)[未睇晒個世界前請不要有事]二月北歐+倫敦旅行相集","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:58:39.000Z","uid":36475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03293be8b3f585095c71ee7178c9ddeaaa639526","tid":1605300,"uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"臨近生日Party<br />\n想提醒大家世界重有好多靚人靚景等緊你<br />\n希望大家記得要平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>原文</ins><br />\n<del>重有一個學期就畢業(如無意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</del>我真係畢到業同搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係唔會有Gap year嘅人嚟<br />\n所以趁最後一個假期用晒啲里數一個人去一次歐洲旅行(第一次去咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n今次19日旅程遇到好多好人好事<br />\n雖然亦有好多唔好彩但總括而言都係一次好值得好開心嘅旅程<br />\n所有相都有執過同用Sony A7(第一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)影<br />\n鏡就FE 55mm F1.8 ZA 同 Voigtlander 15mm f/4.5 ver. I<br />\n我個人比較重手因為我主要係想將我當時嘅感受重現<br />\n色彩都係表達嘅一環所以唔寫實請見諒<br />\n因為用相表達為主所以我都唔多講只會標地名同可能有少少註解<br />\n<br />\n可聽住旅行歌代入下心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有中文字幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JtysZiVN7Eo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJtysZiVN7Eo&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=926aac6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JtysZiVN7Eo</a><br />\n<br />\nNorway In A Nutshell - 挪威縮影<br />\nClassic route, 由Oslo出發 &gt; Myrdal &gt; Fl&aring;m &gt; Bergen終點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7812/40126821473_ce4c50e710_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7847/33216545258_dd4f3149dc_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7834/47039360212_a7ed5557ff_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7878/40126816083_11be354138_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7870/33216530328_1e158f29e6_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7925/33216536728_713b13048f_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7927/40126812103_acdc5877d7_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7904/40126811403_70cea97b82_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7859/46177921175_ac3e0af23a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7859%2F46177921175_ac3e0af23a_b.jpg&h=e1180e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOslo - 奧斯陸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7848/46403605044_bf517289f9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7848%2F46403605044_bf517289f9_b.jpg&h=f65ddb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7802/33251906728_8626eb3db0_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7906/47127260481_7c738e9936_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7906%2F47127260481_7c738e9936_b.jpg&h=3e4eefc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7903/32185125607_ef6230a7e2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7903%2F32185125607_ef6230a7e2_b.jpg&h=1f112817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTromso - 特羅姆瑟<br />\n極光個到其實眼睇只係灰光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7849/40146641173_328a63a039_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7839/40146645833_e8b95fc5c3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7839%2F40146645833_e8b95fc5c3_b.jpg&h=b99d9e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7893/46387695484_7ea56dcaf3_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7878/46197484905_3a7e3568bf_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7878%2F46197484905_3a7e3568bf_b.jpg&h=f4da81eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7816/32169340737_712028619f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7816%2F32169340737_712028619f_b.jpg&h=fe37b03f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7864/32169341367_c7fccdb8f3_b.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCopenhagen - 哥本哈根<br />\nStunning, 一個將古今融合得好出色嘅城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7846/33189009978_0e2a39fe12_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7846%2F33189009978_0e2a39fe12_b.jpg&h=707cf1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7823/40099068963_418f2d716b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7823%2F40099068963_418f2d716b_b.jpg&h=00a81427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7872/32122223317_52c009a3a8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7872%2F32122223317_52c009a3a8_b.jpg&h=e88d88e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7873/40099314953_9a50de09db_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7873%2F40099314953_9a50de09db_b.jpg&h=48e56418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7850/32122398147_f224a25c3a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7850%2F32122398147_f224a25c3a_b.jpg&h=12c6d9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7890/32122418517_88e2c9491f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7890%2F32122418517_88e2c9491f_b.jpg&h=77c30203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7904/46340293484_808194b52b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7904%2F46340293484_808194b52b_b.jpg&h=ac192a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7864/46150505285_22e9ec4614_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7864%2F46150505285_22e9ec4614_b.jpg&h=c5967980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7833/46340294284_35229cf3e2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7833%2F46340294284_35229cf3e2_b.jpg&h=8234089a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7916/32122421227_7c7a4482d1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7916%2F32122421227_7c7a4482d1_b.jpg&h=96a291e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7917/46340291994_c0ed2e3cbb_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7917%2F46340291994_c0ed2e3cbb_b.jpg&h=83092c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7867/40099280133_55565abfb4_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7867%2F40099280133_55565abfb4_b.jpg&h=bbe81d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7830/32122396347_604594aac8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7830%2F32122396347_604594aac8_b.jpg&h=b5cac88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStockholm - 斯德哥爾摩<br />\n其實旅程第三日就病咗, 由其係係Stockholm個兩日特別嚴重因為就係係去Stockholm嘅郵輪上病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但宜家諗返當日死頂出去無休息係好值得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7866/46315139384_e5d1d623e3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7866%2F46315139384_e5d1d623e3_b.jpg&h=cefce473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7826/32097411057_265d002a88_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7826%2F32097411057_265d002a88_b.jpg&h=6643851d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7913/46315139314_703cca670c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7913%2F46315139314_703cca670c_b.jpg&h=fc43c0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7879/46315139564_120b7a480a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7879%2F46315139564_120b7a480a_b.jpg&h=16e10c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7884/47039209801_cf23553106_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7884%2F47039209801_cf23553106_b.jpg&h=27a89006&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da41af222efdf4ca561ae9c5c34d54b8be246b7f","tid":1605300,"uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"Helsinki - 赫爾辛基<br />\n北歐四國中芬蘭同另外三國感覺上係格格不入, 可能因為畀俄羅斯統治過, 但因而有種獨特嘅感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7843/40180990843_daea780394_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7843%2F40180990843_daea780394_b.jpg&h=c5afc23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br 